Package employees

Class Keeper

java.lang.Object
employees.Keeper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Employee, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AssistantKeeper, HeadKeeper
public class Keeper extends Object implements Employee, Serializable
This is the generic class for Clyde Conservation Keepers

This class do not have a specific constructor as it is designed with inheritance in mind.

Because this class is used as a Parent class, it does not allow the use of a private constructor to restrict object creation

Author:
Erik
